Hi, I am a beginner in HubSpot React CMS. I am trying to use the slick slider in HubSpot React CMS, but I face an error while adding the &lt;Slider {...settings}&gt; code. If anyone has a solution, please let me know. <https://prnt.sc/URGJ6I_cTu_F>
```import Slider from "react-slick";
import "slick-carousel/slick/slick.css";
import "slick-carousel/slick/slick-theme.css";

const App = () =&gt; {
    const settings = {
        dots: true,
        speed: 500,
        slidesToShow: 1,
        slidesToScroll: 1,
        infinite: true,
        autoplay: true,
        autoplaySpeed: 1000,
    };

    return (
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;h2&gt;Carousel Component&lt;/h2&gt;
            &lt;Slider {...settings}&gt;
                &lt;div&gt;
                    &lt;h3&gt;FIRST SLIDE&lt;/h3&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;div&gt;
                    &lt;h3&gt;SECOND SLIDE&lt;/h3&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;div&gt;
                    &lt;h3&gt;THIRD SLIDE&lt;/h3&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;div&gt;
                    &lt;h3&gt;FORTH SLIDE&lt;/h3&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/Slider&gt;
        &lt;/div &gt;
    );
};

export default App;```
